{"lastModified":1775228215053,"uri":"c::7819307041::vessel::d5cc7768-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: Greece\n\nONEIDA yacht is a 52.0 ft long sailboat catamaran. It was built by Lagoon in 2020. The yacht layout features 5 cabins and accommodates 10 guests. The cabin arrangement is following: 5 VIP cabins, all with private facilities and fully airconditioned.","blueprint":{"name":"ONEIDA","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7768-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::bee68f80-1ab1-11f0-aebe-2d1b9680e6db/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7768-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::bf10acc0-1ab1-11f0-aebe-2d1b9680e6db/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7768-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::bee90080-1ab1-11f0-aebe-2d1b9680e6db/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7768-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::bf0fe970-1ab1-11f0-aebe-2d1b9680e6db/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7768-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::befadad0-1ab1-11f0-aebe-2d1b9680e6db/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7768-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::bf0eb0f0-1ab1-11f0-aebe-2d1b9680e6db/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7768-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::bedb1dd0-1ab1-11f0-aebe-2d1b9680e6db/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7768-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::bf0f9b50-1ab1-11f0-aebe-2d1b9680e6db/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7768-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::bed29250-1ab1-11f0-aebe-2d1b9680e6db/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7768-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::bf1085b0-1ab1-11f0-aebe-2d1b9680e6db/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7768-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::bef77f70-1ab1-11f0-aebe-2d1b9680e6db/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7768-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::bf103790-1ab1-11f0-aebe-2d1b9680e6db/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7768-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::bf0cb520-1ab1-11f0-aebe-2d1b9680e6db/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7768-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::bee44590-1ab1-11f0-aebe-2d1b9680e6db/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7768-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::bf0eff10-1ab1-11f0-aebe-2d1b9680e6db/{imageVariant}"],"make":"Lagoon","model":"Lagoon 52 F","maxCrew":3,"sleeps":10,"basePort":{"uri":"a::place::f8079970-5bf8-11f0-b250-a14aba6c4f33","name":"Nea Peramos Marina","coordinates":{"latitude":37.99993867559947,"longitude":23.42040940867487},"country":"Greece"},"builtYear":2020,"architect":"","interiorDesigner":"","refitYear":"","topSpeed":10,"cruiseSpeed":8,"fuelCapacity":0,"cabinLayout":[{"label":"VIP Cabins","value":"5"}],"cabins":5,"bathrooms":5,"length":15.85,"beam":8.63,"draft":1.25,"hullType":"Catamaran","hullConstruction":"","superStructure":[],"engines":"2 x 80 HP (Yanmar 4JH80)","amenities":[{"label":"Air Conditioning"},{"label":"Bimini"},{"label":"Deck Shower"},{"label":"Generator"},{"label":"Inverter"},{"label":"Water Maker"},{"label":"Ice Maker"}],"toys":[{"label":"Water Skis Adult"},{"label":"Water Skis Kids"},{"label":"Tube"},{"label":"Wake Board"},{"label":"SU Paddle Boards","quantity":"2"},{"label":"Fishing Gear"}],"entertainment":["Salon Tv","Salon Stereo","Onboard WIFI"],"tenders":["AB 4,20 - YANMAR 40hp"]},"crew":[{"name":"Sotiris Drokalos","avatar":"/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7768-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::7209bde0-1ab1-11f0-a371-d301237a67f9/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"His name is Sotiris but everyone calls him \"Captain SO.\"\n\nEverything he knows about himself is that he loves the sea, that he was born near it, that he lives by and for it. His sailing experience began when he was ten years old, thanks to his father who bought him his first windsurf. This is when he decided to follow his dream of becoming a seafarer.\nHe has spent more than ten years as a captain on a variety of sailing vessels in the Atlantic Ocean and the Mediterranean Sea.\n\nBecause of his sailing experience, calmness, dedication, and vigilance, he can safely sail you under any circumstances and he will do my best to ensure that your holiday exceeds your higher expectations!\n\nA bit more of me... S.C.U.B.A. is one of his hobbies. Diving, flying ultralight aircraft, skiing, windsurfing, playing the guitar, playing and designing board games are all things he enjoys doing but ultimately, all he does is spend his free time with his 3-year-old twins.\n\nDon't forget... \"A bad day of sailing is much better than a good day of working\"\nSee you aboard."},{"name":"Gregory Kalaitzakis","role":"Captain","bio":"Gregory is a talented and passionate chef from Greece with a diverse culinary background spanning over 10 years of experience. After completing his studies in Le Monde Culinary School Athens, he has developed ability to create delightful menus according to individual preferences. From creating menus, food management, safety and hygiene standards he is excited to return to the sea and create new dishes and a wonderful dining atmosphere on board. Fluent in both Greek and English, he is committed to providing Oneida guests with an unforgettable gastronomic journey. He specializes in Greek and Mediterranean flavors. Gregory's professional journey includes roles such as Head Chef at notable establishments, where he demonstrated leadership and creativity in culinary arts."}],"pricing":{"weekPricingFrom":{"currency":"EUR","price":1850000,"displayCurrency":"EUR","displayPrice":1850000,"unit":"WEEK"},"weekPricingTo":{"currency":"EUR","price":2250000,"displayCurrency":"EUR","displayPrice":2250000,"unit":"WEEK"},"pricingInfo":[{"name":"Low Season","effectiveDates":[{"from":"2025-01-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2025-05-31T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2026-01-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2026-05-31T23: